description: {"blocks":[{"key":"25obg","text":"Once the co-culture IM plates have grown for four days, it is time to select Sp transformants. Selecting these transformants requires harvesting the cells from the co-culture plates, dislodging and removing any remaining Agro from the culture, and plating Sp onto K1 selection media. In our laboratory, we use 300 mg/L Hygromycin B (Gibco #10687010) as our selection marker. Additionally, we add 50 mg/L Carbenicillin (Carb) and 50 mg/l Tetracycline (Tet) to our K1 plates to kill Agrobacterium. All steps here, with the exception of centrifugation steps, must be carried out in a sterile environment, ideally in the sterile area around an open flame.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"9f8kn","text":"For each plasmid transformed, prepare a 50 mL conical with   of DS solution.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":59,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"fgdvr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"amount","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"amount":"30","error":false,"guid":"C761B6405B5911ED9B066FE432FCA0CB","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"unit":2}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"17rp9","text":"From the appropriate conical for the plate to be harvested, remove   of DS.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":67,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"5017i","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"amount","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"amount":"1","error":false,"guid":"CABE4EC05B5911ED9B066FE432FCA0CB","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"unit":2}}}}
